title: Can you explain a little further?
tags: whole_u_mgmt

Me: Can you explain a little further?

Facilyn: Sure. 

Facilyn: The idea of holism reminds us that the world works as integrated wholes and patterns, not as separate parts stitched together. When you define the whole you’re managing, you start to see how other wholes affect it—and how your choices ripple outward in return.

